metadata.name: Santa Muerta s1
metadata.description:
Santa Muerta, please protect us. Protect us from all shady motherfuckers, backstabbers, liars and cheaters. Keep our families and friends healthy, and protect our bodies and minds from sickness. Protect us from war. Protect us from shady politicians and power hungry diabolic people. Amen. 

Made with AI, Disco Diffusion, After Effects and Photoshop.
